{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_34","type":"agent_message","text":"The actual test behavior is now clear: `4.2.2.Final` depends on `ML-DSA-44`, which is unavailable on GraalVM JDK 21, so JDK 21 can’t reproduce the target issue. The right environment is the repo’s GraalVM JDK 25 build, with `LD_LIBRARY_PATH` pointed at its `lib` directory so `native-image-agent` can load."}}
